{
  "text": "This section is a review of previous results included in Refs. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] , where the vacuum energy-momentum tensor is assumed to be given by the toy model proposed in Refs. [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] based on 2-dimensional massless scalar fields. [CITATION_6] (The solution was presented in different coordinate systems in Ref. [CITATION_7] [CITATION_8] , and here we use the same coordinate system as Ref. [CITATION_9] .) As a preliminary of the review, we introduce the vacuum energy-momentum tensor in Refs. [CITATION_10] [CITATION_11] first.",
